                <p id="pDynamic">You are not static. You are dynamic.</p>
				<p id="pShouldBe">Your eyewear should be, too.</p>
				<p>Ordinary sunwear is optimized to a specific light level &ndash; which is why in certain situations some sunglasses can seem too dark, while other sunglasses are not dark enough.</p>
				<p>Transitions SOLFX sunwear self-adjusts, changing the level of darkness with the sun so you can look great, see great, and perform at your best.</p>
